data.description: Step into the charm of yesteryear with this timeless 4-bedroom, 2-bath bi-level home. The allure of this older residence is complemented by a newly renovated kitchen, blending classic character with modern convenience. A testament to care and craftsmanship, this property invites you to create new memories while savoring the vintage charm that makes it truly special. Embrace the warmth of a bygone era in this lovingly preserved home, where history meets modern comfort.
